<view class="containars">
  <form bindsubmit="formSubmit" bindreset="formReset">

    <view class="canvas_title">
      当前积分比例
    </view>
    <view class="canvas">
      <canvas style="width: 160px; height: 160px;" canvas-id="ring"></canvas>
    </view>
    <view class='waring'>
      修改积分比例为：
    </view>

    <view class='input'>
      <input name="rate_customer" bindchange='changeRateCustomer' placeholder='请输入数字' type='number' maxlength='2' value='{{rate_customer}}'></input>
      <view class='posab'>
        %
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class='warings'>
      <view class='waring_title'>
        提示
      </view>
      <view class='text'>
        该积分是指消费者在本店消费后，本店将返还给消费者一定比例的积分。
      </view>
      <view class='text'>
        返还部分的积分平台将从商家结算款项中扣除。
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="button flex_between">
      <button formType="reset">取消</button>
      <button class="submit" formType="submit">确定</button>
    </view>
  </form>
</view>